<div class="fn" id="FN1">
<p id="P1">Authors’ Contributions</p>
<p id="P2">MAS, MJS, SCY, NP, DM, GH and PBR contributed to study design, implementation and execution, data analysis and interpretation and paper writing. HMK, RC, CGR and JD contributed to data interpretation and paper writing.</p>
</div>
<div class="fn" id="CR1">
<sup>*</sup><p class="display-inline">Corresponding authors: <span>msuchard@ucla.edu</span>, <span>ryan@ohdsi.org</span></p>
